{"id":56160,"name":"Twitter Remove Trends, Ads and User Recomendations","description":"Twitterからトレンド、広告、おすすめユーザー、プロモートツイートを非表示にするためのスクリプト。\r\n日本語のハッシュタグきもすぎ＼(^o^)／\r\n\r\n===================================\r\n\r\nThis style remove User Recomendations, Trends and PROMOTED TWEET on Twitter.\r\nAnd also can remove Ads in any languages.","user":{"id":25589,"name":"SpicyCarrotSalad","email":"masashi.iwao@gmail.com","paypal_email":"masashi.iwao@gmail.com","homepage":null,"about":null,"license":null},"updated":"2014-04-29T07:19:36.000Z","weekly_install_count":1,"total_install_count":1662,"rating":1.0,"after_screenshot_name":"https://userstyles.org/style_screenshots/56160_after.png?r=1687507280","obsoleting_style_id":null,"obsoleting_style_name":null,"obsolete":0,"admin_delete_reason_id":null,"obsoletion_message":null,"screenshots":null,"license":null,"created":"2011-11-11T04:36:02.000Z","category":"site","raw_subcategory":"twitter","subcategory":"twitter","additional_info":"Apr 29, 2014\r\n新デザインのプロフィールページに対応\r\n\r\nOct 20, 2013\r\nDashboard(左カラム)を固定する設定を追加\r\n\r\nJan 14, 2013\r\nPromo Tweetの仕様変更に対応\r\n\r\nSep 16, 2012 Rev.2\r\nTwitterの検索クエリーの仕様変更に対応\r\nPromo Tweetの仕様変更に対応\r\n\r\nAug 26, 2012\r\n広告非表示、おすすめユーザー非表示の指定を修正\r\n日本語ハッシュタグのみを非表示にするオプションを追加\r\n#の直後に日本語がくる場合のみ非表示できるので\r\n#の直後に数字やアルファベットが来る場合は非表示に出来ません\r\n\r\nMar 23, 2012\r\nPromo Tweetの指定を div[data-item-id*=\":\"] から div[data-item-id*=\"-\"] に変更\r\n\r\nMar 5, 2012\r\nPromo Tweetの指定にdata-item-idを使うように変更\r\nUse data-item-id attribute to select Promo Tweet\r\n\r\n\r\nFeb 1, 2012\r\nPromo Tweetの非表示機能を追加\r\nAdded Remove Promo Tweet Option\r\n\r\nJan 9, 2012\r\n要素の指定方法をより正確にできるように変更","style_tags":[],"css":"@namespace url(http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml);\r\n\r\n/* Last Modified on Apr 29, 2014. \r\n * See Change log. http://userstyles.org/styles/56160/ */\r\n\r\n@-moz-document domain(\"twitter.com\") {\r\n/* Remove Ads */\r\n/*[[ads]]*/\r\n/* Remove User Recommendations */\r\n/*[[urecomend]]*/\r\n/* Remove Trends */\r\n/*[[t